snippet.title: Galactic Blitz for the Commodore VIC-20 / Commodore VC-20
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Galactic Blitz is an action game set in space.

You have to shoot a lot of aliens, that have sometimes really weird and unfitting shapes (like, for example, a heart) and then eventually advance to the next level...that is if you don't get shot.
